      "raw_text": "SAN FRANCISCO, Dec. 1.-the\nannouncement was made today\nthat the long hoped for conference\nbetween the traffic officers of the\nSouthern Pacific and Santa Fe and\nthe representatives of the Califor-\nmia shippers would be held here\nbeginning tomorrow.\n\n\nThe shippers are protesting\nagainst a threatened increase In\ntranscontinental freight rates.\nWhile 1t is not believed that tho\neast and west bound traffic win ba\nplaced back on the old schedule,\nthere are reasons to hope that Q\nradical and sweeping change will\nbe made in rates on traffic in both\ndirections."
